And then that final piece of like, how do we allow for community participation in projects like what we have coming up with the McGlynn playground?

104
00:11:39,871 --> 00:11:42,733
What does that look like and how would it work?

105
00:11:43,553 --> 00:11:45,055
So those are the four buckets,

106
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:53,784
Um, you know, Belmont, I think had maybe two of these buckets, but as I thought through it, um, I thought this really covered all the bases around naming.

