169
00:19:51,113 --> 00:20:17,407
One thing that I did put in this policy that I want to call your attention to is if we're talking about the idea of a naming committee, there is, and this was, I believe this was in Belmont's policy as well, a final mention that the school committee will adopt a name by a majority vote and that the school committee is not required to accept the recommendation of the naming advisory committee.

170
00:20:17,427 --> 00:20:19,288
That was in fact,

171
00:20:20,363 --> 00:20:24,286
how we established our last naming advisory committee.

172
00:20:25,126 --> 00:20:44,182
And the reason for that to be there is not to say that the school committee would want to waste the time of the volunteers on a naming advisory committee and then blatantly disregard their recommendations.

173
00:20:45,752 --> 00:20:49,454
to acknowledge that the responsibility of this does rest with the school committee.

174
00:20:49,494 --> 00:21:11,342
And if for some reason the school committee felt like the outcome of the advisory committee was compromised or did not align with information that was available to the school committee, the school committee has the authority under the law and would be certainly able to make a different decision about the name.

175
00:21:11,582 --> 00:21:12,722
So that's why that's there.

176
00:21:12,742 --> 00:21:14,183
I just wanted to call that to your attention.

177
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:22,288
Um, and, um, if anyone, I don't know if any of the members have anything they want to say about that.

178
00:21:22,308 --> 00:21:25,371
No.

179
00:21:26,593 --> 00:21:27,974
Sure.

180
00:21:28,414 --> 00:21:31,617
There are certain types of things which we have authority to delegate.

181
00:21:32,918 --> 00:21:34,619
We do much of that with the superintendent.

182
00:21:34,679 --> 00:21:39,403
But for instance, there are certain things that we approve each year that we can't delegate to the superintendent.

183
00:21:39,503 --> 00:21:41,124
Like we have to approve the handbooks.

184
00:21:41,964 --> 00:21:45,507
