00:59:46,129 --> 00:59:47,251
Roll call, member Hayes?

509
00:59:47,812 --> 00:59:48,032
Yes.

510
00:59:48,994 --> 00:59:49,675
Member Rossell?

511
00:59:50,336 --> 00:59:50,556
Yes.

512
00:59:51,418 --> 00:59:51,999
Member Graham?

513
00:59:52,159 --> 00:59:53,922
Yes.

